<subSubSection id="25EB80F9FFD11D17FF77CBBBFE9AFEEC" pageId="11" pageNumber="10" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="6D4ED372FFD11D17FF77CBBBFE9AFEEC" blockId="11.[192,1440,214,309]" pageId="11" pageNumber="10">
<emphasis id="5F850F60FFD11D17FF77CBBBFEC2FF29" bold="true" box="[192,324,214,240]" pageId="11" pageNumber="10">Etymology.</emphasis>
This species is dedicated to our friend Gérard L. Tavakilian (MNHN) in recognition of his many contributions to the knowledge of the 
<taxonomicName id="AAF1A8F1FFD11D17FDC6CB95FC92FECB" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1802" box="[625,788,248,274]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="10" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Cerambycidae</taxonomicName>
, and for his frequent, willing consultation and help to the authors.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
